Third-party components
================================================================================

This project orchestrates several third-party software components,
each distributed under its own license. THIS REPOSITORY NEITHER
REDISTRIBUTES NOR BUNDLES ANY OF THEIR BINARIES OR SOURCE — every
component is either installed through its upstream distribution
channel (Homebrew cask, GitHub Releases, upstream CDN) or downloaded
at setup time from the vendor. No third-party source is vendored into
the repo tree; see `.gitignore`, which excludes `vendor/`, `*.dll`,
`*.exe`, `*.so`, and `.wine-*`.

