--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Wine (stable)
    License: LGPL-2.1-or-later
    Source:  https://www.winehq.org/
    Notes:   Installed via Homebrew Cask `wine-stable` (Gcenx build).
             The optional `-fvisibility=default` rebuild clones upstream
             Wine source from https://gitlab.winehq.org/wine/wine at
             tag `wine-11.0`, builds locally, and copies only
             `dlls/winemac.drv/winemac.so` over the Homebrew cask.
             The original winemac.so is preserved as
             winemac.so.gcenx-backup.

